reviews.text:
opened by a shanghai-ese. food is authentic and reasonably priced. 
lunch and dinner set is only 48HKD comes with a dish, vegetable rice and soy milk. what a bargain.
the xiaolongbao is my favourite. thin clear skin. yummy 😋
opened till late, best for a late supper :)
Always reliable. Good hygiene. Delicious food.
As a Shanghainese, I have to say this one is one of the most authentic Shanghainese restaurants in HK.  Plus the price is very reasonable. Xiaolong Bao and guotie are v good.

result.name: 客尚來

reviews.text: 地方太細，並不太整潔，食材一般
上海菜，幫襯好多年，食物OK，睌市有套餐，$48-$70，(一飯、一餸、一杯豆漿)首選套餐有口水雞、醉雞、鱔鰗、醬爆雞丁、回鍋肉、虾仁炒蛋，話梅骨…………經濟實惠。唯一缺點係地方細，挫得好擠迫。

價錢偏貴，質素每況愈下， 廚餘般既食材
比以前剛開業的時候差得多了
不推薦之選，如果你想要感受大陸質素
